* **Equities (US Russ 2000 & Micro E-mini Nasdaq-100):** Both indices show high adaptivity. The Russell 2000 generated +61,110.47 USD (99.65% win rate), while the Nasdaq-100 returned +21,806.50 USD. Both charts reflect steady, programmatic equity expansion with minimal downside deviation.


